# ðŸŽ¹ Simple Piano App

A browser-based piano built with React and Tone.js. Play notes using your keyboard or mouse with realistic audio and visual feedback.

---

## Features

- Interactive piano keys (click or press keys to play)
- Keyboard support for white and black keys
- Audio synthesis powered by [Tone.js](https://tonejs.github.io/)
- Visual feedback for pressed keys
- Clean, responsive layout with CSS

---

## Key Bindings

| Key | Note |
|-----|------|
| a   | C    |
| s   | D    |
| d   | E    |
| f   | F    |
| g   | G    |
| h   | A    |
| j   | B    |
| w   | C#   |
| e   | D#   |
| t   | F#   |
| y   | G#   |
| u   | A#   |

---

## Setup

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/npanitz/simple-piano-app.git
   cd simple-piano-app
   npm install
   npm start
